chapterList.JSParser: function functionName(config, params, result) {    let list = [];    let xpath = params.nativeTool.XPathParserWithSource(result);    let res = xpath.queryWithXPath("//div[contains(@class,\"module-tab-item tab-item\")]");    let playSrcList = [];    // ÂèñÂá∫Á∫øË∑ØÂêçÁß∞‰∏éÁ¥¢Âºï    res.forEach((x, i) => {        let attr = x.attributes();        let title = attr['data-dropdown-value'];        playSrcList.push(title);    });    let sortItem = xpath.queryWithXPath("//div[contains(@class,\"module-play-list-content\")]");    sortItem.forEach((x, i) => {        let itemList = x.queryWithXPath("//a");        itemList.forEach(a => {            let attr = a.attributes();            list.push({                "title": playSrcList[i] + '- ' + a.content(),                "url": attr.href,            });        });    });    return { 'list': list };}
